part of our body

00:04:35.570 --> 00:04:37.580 align:middle line:90%
and every organ in our body.

00:04:37.580 --> 00:04:39.470 align:middle line:84%
And really, the
decision not to forgive

00:04:39.470 --> 00:04:41.252 align:middle line:90%
is really a decision to suffer.

00:04:41.252 --> 00:04:42.710 align:middle line:84%
And when we do
forgive, it's really

00:04:42.710 --> 00:04:44.930 align:middle line:84%
