00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:52.010 align:middle line:90%
We can be together again.

00:04:52.010 --> 00:04:55.310 align:middle line:84%
The other person may not change,
but we can't change the pain

00:04:55.310 --> 00:04:58.100 align:middle line:84%
that we're carrying on, and
that's what forgiveness is.

00:04:58.100 --> 00:05:00.590 align:middle line:84%
It's a releasing of the
painful past in ourselves.

00:05:00.590 --> 00:05:03.170 align:middle line:84%
